  "img": "https://assets.forge-vtt.com/bazaar/core/icons/commodities/materials/bowl-liquid-white.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>shows brief visions of the past</em></p><hr /><p><em>Wondrous item</em></p>\n<p>While this bowl is filled with water, you can use an action to speak the bowl's command word and summon a <em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.monsters.Actor.namJz755U1EhvEJa]{Water Elemental}</em>, as if you had cast the <em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.1LkZvINag7KqBmDR]{Conjure Elemental}</em> spell. The bowl can't be used this way again until the next dawn.</p>\n<p>The bowl is about 1 foot in diameter and half as deep. It weighs 3 pounds and holds about 3 gallons.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
